<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  .body { font-family: 'Helvetica', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; }
  .card { max-width: 500px; background: #ffffff; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
  .header { background-color: #3f51b5; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
  .content { padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
  .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #999; text-align: center; padding: 20px; }
  .btn { background: #3f51b5; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; }
</style>
</head>
<body class="body">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="{{logoUrl}}" width="120" alt="Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h1 style="color: #3f51b5;">Congratulations, {{firstName}}!</h1>
      <p>Today marks your <strong>{{yearsCount}} year</strong> anniversary with {{company}}.</p>
      <p>Your trust and dedication have been invaluable. We are honored to have you on our platform!</p>
      <br>
      <a href="{{logoUrl}}" class="btn">View Our Milestones</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">Â© {{year}} {{company}}</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
